Here's a production-ready `.gitignore` for a **C++23 + CMake + Vulkan + AAA Game Engine**.

```
# ==========================
# Build Output
# ==========================
[Bb]uild/
[Bb]in/
[Ll]ib/
[Oo]ut/
[Dd]ist/
cmake-build-*/
CMakeFiles/
CMakeCache.txt
cmake_install.cmake
compile_commands.json
Makefile
install_manifest.txt

# ==========================
# Visual Studio
# ==========================
.vs/
*.VC.db
*.VC.opendb
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.ncb
*.aps
*.pch
*.ipch
*.ilk
*.idb
*.pdb
*.opendb

# ==========================
# VS Code
# ==========================
.vscode/

# ==========================
# CLion / JetBrains
# ==========================
.idea/

# ==========================
# Xcode
# ==========================
DerivedData/
*.xcworkspace
*.xcuserdata

# ==========================
# Object Files
# ==========================
*.o
*.obj
*.lo
*.a
*.lib
*.dll
*.so
*.dylib
*.exe
*.exp

# ==========================
# Logs
# ==========================
*.log
logs/

# ==========================
# Temporary Files
# ==========================
*.tmp
*.temp
*.bak
*.old
*.orig

# ==========================
# Runtime Cache
# ==========================
Cache/
Caches/
Saved/
Intermediate/
DerivedDataCache/
ShaderCache/
PipelineCache/
AssetCache/
ThumbnailCache/

# ==========================
# Generated Files
# ==========================
Generated/
AutoGenerated/
GeneratedCode/

# ==========================
# Shader Files
# ==========================
*.spv
*.dxc
*.dxil
*.metallib

# ==========================
# Crash Dumps
# ==========================
CrashReports/
*.dmp

# ==========================
# Profiling
# ==========================
Profiler/
Profiling/
Traces/
Captures/

# ==========================
# Python
# ==========================
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/

# ==========================
# Testing
# ==========================
Testing/
CTestTestfile.cmake

# ==========================
# Package Managers
# ==========================
conanbuild/
conaninfo.txt
vcpkg_installed/

# ==========================
# Operating System
# ==========================
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store

# ==========================
# Archives
# ==========================
*.zip
*.7z
*.rar
*.tar
*.gz

# ==========================
# Editor Backup Files
# ==========================
*~
*.swp
*.swo
```

This is a solid starting point for an engine repository and covers the common generated files from CMake, Visual Studio, Vulkan shader compilation, caches, logs, profiling, and temporary files. As your build system evolves, you can add any engine-specific generated directories (for example, `Cooked/`, `Binaries/`, or `DerivedData/`) if needed.
